channel.title: Help!
channel.description: Alright so I just downloaded CaliberScape V1 and in some of the shops it sells some of the new items like 3rd age and skill-capes. Everytime i click on trade for one of those shops with a new item in it, it freezes. I play on the Moparscape 3.2/with aryan. I'm I using a wrong server to play on? Also when i click on the "runserver" option it just opens a command prompt, no client to play on. So can somebody please help me. I would really appreciate any help at all! Thank-you. :)
